cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving neural machine translation systems. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as NMT is a subfield of machine learning. Additionally, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible sub-category as NMT is a type of AI. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with improving neural networks. Finally, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely sub-category as it is not directly related to the content of the paper, but it could be relevant if the proposed approach is applied to image captioning tasks.
